name: Shenzhen Vinstar photoelectricity CO.,LTD
overview:
Founded in 2006, Vinstar LED lighting has become a leading manufacturer specialized in LED lighting products in China.In the past years,we focus on design,research,development and production of indoor and outdoor LED lighting products.

We provide a wide variety of products, including LED Bulb, Dimmable bulbs light, Solar bulb light, LED Tube, LED Panel lights, Spotlights, LED down lights, LED wall lights, LED street lights, LED floodlights, LED wall washer and more. All these LED lighting products are energy efficient and eco-friendly.

Vinstar is equipped with advanced SMT equipment, and boosts an annual production capacity of 1,200,000 units. We also have strong OEM/ODM capabilities, after service, skilled workers, excellent quality management as well as professional brand strategy. We run our factory under the guidance of ISO 9001:2008, and comply with our own strict production standards, laws and statutes of the People’s Republic of China. Nowadays we quallified our prdoucts with CE, RoHS, FCC, TUV and UL and ensure 3 years’ warranty.We promise to provide competitive prices, top quality, fast delivery and excellent services for our partner.
